<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1912-07-16T18:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1912-07-16T18:00:00-05:00" n="1582" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d1582">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 819.00/432.</note>
                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">American Minister</gloss> to
                                the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss></hi>.</head>
                        <opener>
                            <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                        </opener>
                        <opener>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">
                                <placeName>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>, <lb/>
                                    <hi rend="italic">Panama</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1912-07-16T18:00:00-05:00">
                                    <hi rend="italic">July 16, 1912—6 p.m.</hi>
                                </date>
                            </dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>Nearly all the supervisors have been heard from. They report satisfactory
                            and orderly elections on 14th, Diaz party not voting.</p>
                        <p>Yesterday rowdies in Panama committed numerous outrages, none so far as
                            known upon Americans. I have impressed upon Minister for Foreign Affairs
                            urgent necessity for promptly stopping this, which is apparently
                            countenanced by the police.</p>
                        <closer>
                            <signed>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">Dodge.</hi>
                            </signed>
                        </closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>